THE_THEME_IS_SECRET_DESC:
Australia is one of the first places around the world to know the theme, because we're ahead in terms of time zones compared with the rest of the world.

Therefore you must not share the theme on any public medium, including social media (Twitter, Facebook, etc.) or give it away on any public website (e.g. by creating a GitHub repository with the theme inside it or in the name).

The organisers will let everyone know when the last jam location has received the theme, and when you can publically talk about it.
